summary: MANEKI - Welcome to Maneki, where prosperity meets opportunity. Inspired by the revered Japanese symbol of good fortune, this token embodies the spirit of luck and success. Utilizing 0x8888 in the contract, a number considered highly auspicious in Japan, we infuse each transaction with the power of prosperity. Join our community and embark on a journey guided by confidence and optimism. May your financial destiny be illuminated by the charm of the Maneki cat.
